{"tid":1890481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全部武漢肺炎YouTube 片都會黃標","createTime":"2020-02-21T08:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T11:33:11.000Z","uid":80972,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f2bd59f3cc97aac35485b77ad9086a3b018940b8","tid":1890481,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"YouTube 已經classify 左武肺做sensitive event，全部相關影片都會有黃標<br />\n意思係佢覺得廣告商唔鍾意喺呢d片落廣告<br />\n<br />\n解決方法:<br />\n1) 全世界都同YouTube投訴，話我地想喺武肺片睇廣告，咁黃藍YouTuber都會有錢賺。不過我唔認為YouTube 會理<br />\n2) 拍片同所有文字唔提&quot;武漢肺炎&quot;或相關字眼，比如黑警中招唔使提中咩，大家都明啦。可以揾人試下，work唔work。不過避到machine，YouTube 都可以人手審查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdvertiser-friendly content guidelines:<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/6162278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fyoutube%2Fanswer%2F6162278&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b5b336eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/6162278</a><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\nYouTube 個creator channel有公布classify 左武肺做sensitive event\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dZ7lV8UPLJM&amp;t=278s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdZ7lV8UPLJM%26t%3D278s&d=8qD7g5vOfNqkLkogRxTPVP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=10c45f18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dZ7lV8UPLJM&amp;t=278s</a>"},{"pid":"a7530fef88b2aef905e36ddc5d414c5ad1259d40","tid":1890481,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ec1fe867df10dce3545d692b9dd1f059dadd9d70","tid":1890481,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"04f613959ec0286c43c37359cf6a1035ee2a9d09","tid":1890481,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"d0dc22aeddf5cc6c46f9a178f01b6247ce56f538","tid":1890481,"uid"